  :topic: Chapter7/length
  :from_source: T
  :language: cpp
  :caption: Finding the length of a string

  The active code below outputs the length of string ``fruit``.
  ~~~~
  #include <iostream>
  using namespace std;

  int main() {
      string fruit = "Watermelon";
      int length;
      length = fruit.length();
      cout << length << endl;
  }